# A Simple Way to make a Customizable Pong Game in Python.
***
## Instructions: 
- Left Player: W to move up, S to move down 
- Right Player: Up Arrow to move up, Down Arrow to move up 
- Required Packages: Pygame
***
## Files:
- Two sounds for winning,
- Success Sound, 
- Bat Sound, 
- Font file (.ttf),

